videos.description: Washington's Malik Dime gets a block on Arizona's Lauri Markkanen and Matisse Thybulle follows it up with a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Washington gets an early spark with block and 3-pointer

videos.description: Arizona's Lauri Markkanen makes an and-1 shot down in the post.
videos.headline: Markkanen gets the and-1 shot to fall from under the rim

videos.description: Washington's Matisse Thybulle loses his shoe on a layup and then tries to make a block at the other end.
videos.headline: Thybulle tries blocking shot while holding shoe

videos.description: Arizona's Allonzo Trier takes it himself for a layup after forcing a Washington turnover.
videos.headline: Trier goes coast-to-coast off steal

videos.description: Arizona's Allonzo Trier slams home a two-handed slam assisted by Rawle Alkins.
videos.headline: Trier throws down double-clutch dunk

videos.description: Postgame Breakdown of Lauri Markkanen's performance in Arizona's 76-68 victory over Washington.
videos.headline: Breaking down Lauri Markkanen's 26-point performance against Washington

videos.description: Lauri Markkanen records a double-double of 26 points and 13 rebounds as No. 5 Arizona defeats Washington 76-68.
videos.headline: Markkanen's double-double lifts Arizona past Washington
